Senior Assistant - Inventory - 1 Opening(s) at null
Posted by: null
Posted date: 05-May
Job Description:KEY RESPONSIBILITIES
1. Inward & Outward
Ensure material inward & outward processes are followed as per SOP and STNs are updated on daily basis before store opening
Continuous follow-up with WH for rev stn updation & inter store transfer updation.
2. PI & Shrinkage Control
Ensure PI & global count schedule is followed.
Achieve shrinkage targets
Ensure the %age of shrinkage is under the norms of 0.30% against Sale
3. Damage Control
Ensure control on reduction of damages in packing, handling and transportation locally
Ensure to reduce damages on floor
Ensure proper handling of Merchandise
4. SOP Adherence
Ensure adherence to SOP and report deviations
Ensure timely accounting and settlement of discrepancies as per SOPnullnullnull
